#: abdessalam-ai-webmcp-pro/abdessalam-ai-webmcp-pro.php:182
msgid ""
"Abdessalam AI WebMCP PRO helps make your WordPress site easier for AI agents "
"and AI-enabled browsers to understand. Instead of forcing an assistant to "
"guess from the visual page, the plugin exposes clear instructions, "
"structured tools, and form labels that tell the agent what actions are "
"available and how to use them."
msgstr ""

